---
title: BeaconLink Authorization Flow
---

flowchart TB

    %% =====================================================
    %% Authenticated Principals
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Principals["Authenticated Principals"]

        User["Human User"]
        Service["Platform Service"]
        Agent["BeaconLink Agent"]
        API["External API"]

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Identity Context
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Identity["Identity Context"]

        Session["Authenticated Session"]

        Claims["Identity Claims"]

        Roles["Roles"]

        Attributes["Attributes"]

        Groups["Groups"]

    end

    User --> Session
    Service --> Session
    Agent --> Session
    API --> Session

    Session --> Claims
    Claims --> Roles
    Claims --> Attributes
    Claims --> Groups

    %% =====================================================
    %% Authorization Request
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Request["Authorization Request"]

        Resource["Requested Resource"]

        Action["Requested Action"]

        Environment["Execution Context"]

        RequestCtx["Authorization Context"]

    end

    Roles --> RequestCtx
    Attributes --> RequestCtx
    Groups --> RequestCtx

    Resource --> RequestCtx
    Action --> RequestCtx
    Environment --> RequestCtx

    %% =====================================================
    %% Policy Evaluation
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph PolicyEngine["Policy Engine"]

        Normalize["Normalize Request"]

        RBAC["RBAC Evaluation"]

        ABAC["ABAC Evaluation"]

        Conditions["Policy Conditions"]

        Risk["Risk Assessment"]

        Decision{"Authorization Decision"}

    end

    RequestCtx --> Normalize

    Normalize --> RBAC
    Normalize --> ABAC

    RBAC --> Conditions
    ABAC --> Conditions

    Conditions --> Risk
    Risk --> Decision

    %% =====================================================
    %% Protected Resources
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Resources["Protected Platform Resources"]

        Control["Control Plane"]

        Deployments["Deployment APIs"]

        Workflows["Workflow Engine"]

        Scheduler["Distributed Scheduler"]

        Secrets["Secret Management"]

        Inventory["Inventory Service"]

        Runtime["Runtime Operations"]

        AuditAPI["Audit APIs"]

    end

    Decision -->|Allow| Control
    Decision -->|Allow| Deployments
    Decision -->|Allow| Workflows
    Decision -->|Allow| Scheduler
    Decision -->|Allow| Secrets
    Decision -->|Allow| Inventory
    Decision -->|Allow| Runtime
    Decision -->|Allow| AuditAPI

    %% =====================================================
    %% Deny Path
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Deny["Access Denied"]

        Reject["Reject Request"]

        Reason["Decision Reason"]

        SecurityLog["Security Audit"]

        Alert["Security Alert"]

    end

    Decision -->|Deny| Reject

    Reject --> Reason
    Reason --> SecurityLog
    SecurityLog --> Alert

    %% =====================================================
    %% Continuous Authorization
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Continuous["Continuous Authorization"]

        SessionCheck["Session Validation"]

        PolicyRefresh["Policy Refresh"]

        ContextUpdate["Context Update"]

        ReEvaluate["Re-Evaluate Policies"]

    end

    Control --> SessionCheck
    Deployments --> SessionCheck
    Workflows --> SessionCheck
    Scheduler --> SessionCheck

    SessionCheck --> PolicyRefresh
    PolicyRefresh --> ContextUpdate
    ContextUpdate --> ReEvaluate

    ReEvaluate --> Decision

    %% =====================================================
    %% Audit & Events
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Observability["Observability"]

        Audit["Authorization Audit"]

        Events["Security Events"]

        Metrics["Authorization Metrics"]

        Dashboard["Security Dashboard"]

    end

    Decision --> Audit

    Audit --> Events
    Audit --> Metrics

    Events --> Dashboard
    Metrics --> Dashboard

    %% =====================================================
    %% Policy Inputs
    %% =====================================================

    Inputs["Policy Inputs

• Identity
• Roles
• Groups
• Attributes
• Resource
• Requested Action
• Time
• Network Context
• Device Context
• Risk Score
• Site Policies
• Organization Policies"]

    Inputs -.-> PolicyEngine

    %% =====================================================
    %% Authorization Principles
    %% =====================================================

    Principles["Authorization Principles

• Default Deny
• Least Privilege
• Explicit Allow
• Policy-Based Decisions
• RBAC + ABAC
• Context-Aware Access
• Continuous Re-Evaluation
• Fully Auditable"]

    Principles -.-> PolicyEngine
    Principles -.-> Continuous

